This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with image style transfer using convolutional neural networks. It also involves optimization of encoder/decoder networks for the purpose of style transfer, which falls under the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories. The paper also mentions the reduction of redundant channels in the encoded feature, which could be related to Multimedia (cs.MM) and Graphics (cs.GR) categories.
